{
  "id": "adv_card_ski_02_02",
  "title": "白石沙季 2話 降板の危機",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ミュージカルの稽古初日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—First day of rehearsal for the musical",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "次のシーンは……声は張るようにして\n身振りはちょっと大げさなくらいで……あっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m supposed to raise my voice in the next scene\nand exaggerate my motion… Oh.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7166.666666666666,
          "startTime": 9.6
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "演出家さん、今日はよろしくお願いします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning‚ director!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.833333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "えっ。演技がかたい……ですか\nす、すみません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? My acting is too rigid?\nI-I’m sorry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "ここはもっとしっとりと、ですか？\nで、でも、台本では明るいイメージだと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Er‚ I should be more mild and reserved here?\nBut the script calls for a bright and sunny image…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.633333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、その場その場での対応力が大事なんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. I have to be flexible and adapt on the fly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、もう一度お願いします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Can we do that again‚ please?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "え、さっきの方がよかった……？\nうーん、うーん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ the one before was better?\nHmm… hmm…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（沙季……かなり苦戦してるな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Saki is struggling.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、やっと休憩です……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*sigh* Finally‚ a break…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様……大丈夫か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey… are you okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい、なんとか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes… I’m fine‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "想定していたよりもずっと沢山指摘を受けて\nびっくりしています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "just surprised at\nhow many times I was corrected.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "他の人はこんなに言われてないのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And I was the only one who was like that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "でも、まだレッスン初日ですしね\n初心者なんだから、とにかくぶつかってみます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it’s just the first day‚ and I’m new to this.\nLet’s just keep at it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "あ、休憩が終わるみたいです\n行ってきますね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ looks like break’s over.\nI’ll be going!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（頑張ってはいるが、やっぱりダメ出しが続くな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Saki is trying hard‚ but the criticisms keep coming.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "うう、こんなはずじゃあ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It wasn’t supposed to be like this…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-ski015.m4a",
      "text": "あんなに勉強したのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I spent so much time preparing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（なんとか出来ないか……ん、待てよ？　全てやり直しに）\n（なってる訳じゃない。そうかそういうことか）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Is there anything that could be done? Wait‚ it’s not like)\n(everything she’s doing is wrong. Ah… I see.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 109.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-ski016.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\nお話ってなんでしょうか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚\nWhat did you want to talk to me about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "まずはレッスン初日、お疲れ様\nだいぶぐったりしてるな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "First‚ good work on your first day of the lesson.\nYou definitely look like you had a long day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-ski017.m4a",
      "text": "そう……ですね。さっき、千紗にメッセしたら\n随分と心配されちゃいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes… I texted Chisa just now‚\nand I guess I made her rather worried.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-ski018.m4a",
      "text": "レッスンの初めの方では、単に私が初心者だから\n指摘されてるんだと思ってました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At first‚ I thought I was being corrected\nonly because I was starting out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-ski019.m4a",
      "text": "でも、後半になってもずっと指摘を受けてるうちに\nどんどん自信がなくなって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But as the rehearsal went on and the criticism kept coming‚\nI began to lose confidence…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-ski020.m4a",
      "text": "もしかしたら\n私の実力では難しいお仕事だったのかもしれません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe this job\nis too hard for me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-ski021.m4a",
      "text": "なんというか\n自分の力を過信してしまっていたような……はぁぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I guess\nI overestimated my own ability… *sigh*",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "思った以上に重症だな……\nまぁ、あれだけダメ出しを受ければ当然か",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re taking it harder than I thought…\nWell‚ I supposed it’s natural to feel that way after being humbled like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.16666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-ski022.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんはどう思いますか？\n私、このお仕事を続けて大丈夫なんでしょうか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you think‚ {user}-san?\nCan I really go on with this role?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.83333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-ski023.m4a",
      "text": "私、人にあんなに怒られたことがなくて……\n勉強したことがまるで通じないのがショックで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve never been scolded like that in my life.\nAll the studying I did was of no use at all…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.73333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-ski024.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたらいいか、分からないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now I’m not sure what to do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-ski025.m4a",
      "text": "このまま迷惑をかけるくらいなら\nいっそ降板した方が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe it would be better for everyone\nif I stepped down…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 184.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "それは違う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but you’ve misunderstood something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-ski026.m4a",
      "text": "……え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…It has?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "努力が通じなくて辛いのは分かる\nでも、沙季はちょっと分析が足りないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand how frustrating it can be to find that all your hard work came up empty.\nBut you’re missing something‚ Saki.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 193.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-ski027.m4a",
      "text": "分析……ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Missing something?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 196.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-ski028.m4a",
      "text": "で、でも！\n私はちゃんと勉強しましたよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "B-but…\nI spent so much time preparing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 200.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "いや、事前準備のことじゃなくて\n今日の演技についてだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s not about preparations.\nIt’s about your acting today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 205.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "沙季は自分の演技を全てひとまとめにして\nダメだと思っているが、そうじゃないと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You clumped all your acting together and thought\neverything you did was no good. But I think‚ in reality‚ it’s a bit different.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 210.316568374634,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-ski029.m4a",
      "text": "でも……あんなに怒られたんですよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I was scolded so much…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 213.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "俺から見るとまた違って見えたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see it differently.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 217.23333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "普段の日常の演技や歌の出来はよかった\n予習も活きているし、稽古中の成長も見られたしな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You were just fine in the everyday scenes and the songs.\nThe preparation showed‚ and I could see you were making progress during the rehearsal.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 223.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-ski030.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうなんですか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "R-really?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 227.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "けど、主人公と相対した時や\n主人公を想って一人喋りをする場面で手こずっていた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But you struggled when you played opposite the hero\nand the monologues about your feelings for the hero.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 232.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "つまり……\n沙季は恋に関わる表現に苦戦してるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Basically…\nYou’re struggling with expressions of love.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 238.16666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-ski031.m4a",
      "text": "あっ\nた、確かにそうですっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah!\nNow that you mention it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 242.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-ski032.m4a",
      "text": "同じように練習していても、主人公と関わる\nシーンはいまいちイメージがわかなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I never quite grasped the scenes with the hero‚\nno matter how many times I practiced…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 248.83333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-ski033.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、恋……恋に関わる表現……\nありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… Expressions of love…\nThank you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 258.26666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-ski034.m4a",
      "text": "今後の指針が見えた気がします\n私、もう少し考えてみます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That was really illuminating.\nI’ll think about this a little more.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 262.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、無理はしないようにな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ just take it easy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 265.26666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_02-ski035.m4a",
      "text": "はい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 268,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
